						<a style="background: rgb(0, 142, 173); padding: 7px 50px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgb(26, 117, 152); border-image: none; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: bold;"
						href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="checkUserForm();">登&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;录</a> </span>
